                <li>Use quick actions (recipe/restaurant/spin again).</li>
            </ol>

            <div class="notice">
                ‚úÖ Privacy-first: this server is built to run without storing personal user data.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px; font-size:1.2rem;">What you get</h2>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="featureCard">
                <h3>üé≤ Random Dinner Picker</h3>
                <p>Pick from the app‚Äôs meal options instantly‚Äîno endless scrolling.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="featureCard">
                <h3>ü§ñ ChatGPT Integration</h3>
                <p>Let ChatGPT brainstorm; the picker chooses from the candidates.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="featureCard">
                <h3>üé® Interactive Widget</h3>
                <p>A fun spin animation that lands on a single clear choice.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="featureCard">
                <h3>‚ö° Quick Actions</h3>
                <p>Jump to recipes/restaurants or spin again in one tap.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mutedLine" style="margin-bottom:0;">
            Open source means you can inspect the code and run your own version.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="footerLinks">
            <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
            <a href="/support">Customer Support</a>
        </div>

        <div class="copyright">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved (except as provided by the open-source license).
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
